 facility is host to world-class performances by students, faculty, guest artists and community members. The Murchison Performing Arts Center features two premiere venues: the Margot and Bill Winspear Performance Hall and the Lyric Theater. Visit Us Murchison Performing Arts Center 415 Avenue C Denton, TX 76203-5017 USA Mail Us Murchison Performing Arts Center UNT College of Music 1155 Union Circle #311367 Denton TX 76203-5017 Contact Us 940-369-7802 mpac.boxoffice@unt.edu Technical issues? Site last updated on January 03, 2017 Disclaimer| AA/EOE/ADA| Privacy| Electronic Accessibility| State of Texas Online| Emergency Preparedness| THECB Online Resume System Student Consumer Information| UNT Compliance Hotline| Governors Committee on People with Disabilities| Texas Veterans Portal| UNT Home Site last updated on January 03, 2017 | Important Links 